{
  "stem": "26486.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Let me get my daughter.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So the police officer was so amazed to see my mother-- she must have been about 70, over 70 years old anyway-- to jump like that that he let her go.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He said, please-- he said, mama, you go and get your daughter.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Go get your daughter.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And then I think that the whole night long, I spoke, the whole night long.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They asked me all kinds of things, of course.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] That was my liberation.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But we didn't have the liberation part with Count Bernadotte.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "You didn't ask me that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After Moabit, then we went to Alex-- to Ravensbruck.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "From Moabit, we went to Ravensbruck.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Right?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Did you go to Ravensbruck, or did you go to Mauthausen?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah, only for-- I told you, only for a few weeks.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't count that even.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't count it because it wasn't really my camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My camp was Ravensbruck.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Well let's talk a little bit about what you saw when you were at Mauthausen.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I saw especially the men.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "More men were working than women.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the men were working-- it-- Mauthausen is built on all kinds-- like-- like hills-- and like how do you call where they dig stones?",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, like-- how do you say that?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I can't say that in English anyway.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Some words, I can't say.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But anyway, that's what it is.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Mauthausen is that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They make all kinds of-- they dig up stones and rocks and all that.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That's what the men did in Mauthausen.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We did very-- they didn't make us hardly work there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We didn't do much.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they weren't-- they weren't so strict in Mauthausen with us because they knew we weren't going to stay there.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
